Thomas F. Helms, Jr.

Age : 76Public asset : 20,966,127 USDLinked companies :  Turning Point Brands Inc -  Special Diversified Opportunities Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Thomas F. Helms, Jr., is Non-Executive Chairman at Turning Point Brands, Inc., Founder at National Tobacco Co. LP, Executive Chairman at Fred Stoker & Sons, Inc., Executive Chairman at North Atlantic Trading Co., Inc., Executive Chairman at RBJ Sales, Inc. and Executive Chairman at Stoker, Inc. Mr. Helms was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by Culbro Corp. and General Manager by Revlon, Inc.



